                                    <p>
                                            To Edit your Event Page, fill in or modify the information in this Form Wizard. For best results on your final page please make sure that all of the images that you want to include in a slider or a section are the same size. For example, if you are creating a Sponsor Logo Slider, make sure that all of your Sponsor Logos are the same size. They should be square. Other image recommendations are below.  </p>
                                            <p>To PREVIEW your page, hit the SAVE DRAFT button, then the PREVIEW button. To save your work and publish your Events page to your website, hit the PUBLISH button.<span class="em">This page uses accordions to display data, just click on the arrows > to open and close the accordions.</span></p> 
                                            
                                            <p>To ensure that your page loads quickly and gets good SEO, use images that have been compressed for the web. Squoosh is a free resource for image compression and is recommended by Google. You can access it here - <a href="https://squoosh.app" title="Squoosh" target="_blank">https://squoosh.app/</a>.
                                            </p>
                                            <p>Here is a list of Images you can upload with the image sizes in pixels.</p>
